Name: Average duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities within a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' for cases that end with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress' across cases with high impact products
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress' grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases involving 'PROD582'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the longest variant path ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases resolved within the same day
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases exceeding average resolution time
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases initiated by 'V30' group resources
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to the next activity for each unique variant
Metric: the average of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` != 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before transitioning to any 'Accepted' status activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases with 'Medium' impact compared to those with 'High' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
